und</i> (see   Germond  )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Guermond de Picquigny was born in 1080, in Picquigny, Somme, Picardie, France, his father, Arnoul de Picquigny, was 20 and his mother, Clémence de Ponthieux, was 12. He had at least 1 daughter with Béatrice de Daours. In 1123, at the age of 43, his occupation is listed as régent du royaume de jérusalem in Jerusalem, Ottoman Empire. He died in 1131, in Sidon, South Lebanon, Lebanon, at the age of 51."},"et":{"1080–1131":"1080–1131","1091–1144":"1091–1144","1118–1164":"1118–1164","1116–1185":"1116–1185","1060–1108":"1060–1108","1068–1115":"1068–1115","1080":"1080","1091":"1091","1131":"1131","1164":"1164","1185":"1185","1060":"1060","1118":"1118","1116":"1116","1115":"1115","1068":"1068","1144":"1144","en 1108":"1108","1123 until 1124":"1123","1108":"1108","Picquigny, France":"Picquigny, Somme, Picardie, Prantsusmaa","Saïda, Liban-Sud, Liban":"Saïda, Liban-Sud, Liibanon","Picquigny, Amiens, Somme, Picardie, France":"Picquigny, Somme, Picardie, Prantsusmaa","Jerusalem, Ottoman Empire":"Jerusalem, Osmanisches Reich"},"fi":{"1080–1131":"1080–1131","1091–1144":"1091–1144","1118–1164":"1118–1164","1116–1185":"1116–1185","1060–1108":"1060–1108","1068–1115":"1068–1115","1080":"1080","1091":"1091","1131":"1131","1164":"1164","1185":"1185","1060":"1060","1118":"1118","1116":"1116","1115":"1115","1068":"1068","1144":"1144","en 1108":"1108","1123 until 1124":"1123","1108":"1108","Picquigny, France":"Picquigny, Somme, Picardie, Ranska","Saïda, Liban-Sud, Liban":"Saïda, Liban-Sud, Libanon","Picquigny, Amiens, Somme, Picardie, France":"Picquigny, Somme, Picardie, Ranska","Jerusalem, Ottoman Empire":"Jerusalem, Osmanisches Reich"},"fr":{"1080–1131":"1080–1131","1091–1144":"1091–1144","1118–1164":"1118–1164","1116–1185":"1116–1185","1060–1108":"1060–1108","1068–1115":"1068–1115","1080":"1080","1091":"1091","1131":"1131","1164":"1164","1185":"1185","1060":"1060","1118":"1118","1116":"1116","1115":"1115","1068":"1068","1144":"1144","